OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar is
OL,7,Fto be made a peer and appointed as a
OL,8,Fminister by Andy Burnham as the new
OL,9,Fprime minister continues his shake-up
OL,10,Fof operations after entering No 10.
OL,12,FMr Sarwar will be elevated to the
OL,13,FLords and is expected to take up a
OL,14,Fministerial post at the revamped
OL,15,FDepartment for Business, Innovation,
OL,16,FScience and Trade, headed by Jonathan
OL,17,FReynolds, sources have told the Press
OL,18,FAssociation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
