CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FIt comes as Mr Burnham made a raft of
OL,7,Fministerial appointments on Tuesday
OL,8,Fnight and after he unveiled his
OL,9,FCabinet, which marked a clearout of
OL,10,Floyalists to his predecessor Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer.
OL,13,FMr Sarwar, who has been Scottish
OL,14,FLabour leader since 2021, was among
OL,15,Fthe first to call for Sir Keir to
OL,16,Fstand down in February.
OL,18,FHe hailed successor Mr Burnham for his
OL,19,F"bold Labour vision" as he entered No
OL,20,F10 this week.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FDowning Street confirmed appointments
OL,7,Fincluding Dan Jarvis, who stepped in
OL,8,Fas Sir Keir's defence secretary when
OL,9,FJohn Healey resigned amid a funding
OL,10,Frow and has been returned to his
OL,11,Fprevious post of security minister.
OL,13,FJames Murray, who was health secretary
OL,14,Fwhen Wes Streeting quit, has been made
OL,15,FFinancial Secretary to the Treasury
OL,16,Fand Paymaster General.
OL,18,FAnna Turley is no longer Labour Party
OL,19,Fchair and has instead been made a Home
OL,20,FOffice minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
