SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FFlorence Eshalomi has become a housing
OL,7,Fminister and Andy Slaughter Solicitor
OL,8,FGeneral, freeing up their roles as
OL,9,Fheads of parliament's housing and
OL,10,Fjustice committees.
OL,12,FThere were also 17 re-appointments for
OL,13,Fministers to remain in their roles,
OL,14,Fincluding Sarah Sackman as justice
OL,15,Fminister and Luke Pollard as defence
OL,16,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
