PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FMr Burnham called for unity told his
OL,7,FCabinet he will lead a "cost-of-living
OL,8,FGovernment" after announcing an #850
OL,9,Fmillion tax cut on electricity bills
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,12,FNo 10 said the Cabinet meeting
OL,13,Freflected "a sense of a united team, a
OL,14,Fnew sense of energy, and a second
OL,15,Fchance at a first impression."
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@KO]uD@KOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
