OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FHis first policy reflected the focus
OL,7,Fon helping hard-pressed people, but
OL,8,Fquestions were raised about how it was
OL,9,Fbeing funded and whether the #45 a
OL,10,Fyear it will save households is
OL,11,Fworthwhile.
OL,13,FThe Government said the electricity
OL,14,Fbill VAT cut would be funded in part
OL,15,Fby scrapping Sir Keir's digital ID
OL,16,Fproject, which had been estimated to
OL,17,Fcost about #600 million a year over
OL,18,Fthree years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FThat falls short of the estimated #850
OL,7,Fmillion hit to tax revenues from the
OL,8,FVAT cut, and funding for digital ID
OL,9,Fwas meant to have come from
OL,10,Funidentified Whitehall savings.
OL,12,FDowning Street has insisted the plan
OL,13,Fis fully funded.
OL,15,FSingle bus fares are to be capped
OL,16,Facross England from January under
OL,17,Ffurther plans, in a further measure to
OL,18,Fbe announced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FIt echoes one of Mr Burnham's policies
OL,7,Fas Greater Manchester mayor, which saw
OL,8,Fhim set up a publicly-run transport
OL,9,Fsystem, bringing local bus services `
OL,10,Fthe Bee Network ` back under public
OL,11,Fownership, with more routes and lower
OL,12,Ffares.
OL,14,FAt Cabinet, Mr Burnham sat opposite
OL,15,Fhis new Chancellor John Healey, and
OL,16,Fwas flanked by Cabinet Secretary Dame
OL,17,FAntonia Romeo and Education Secretary
OL,18,Fand deputy Labour leader Lucy Powell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
