FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784679493
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar to
OL,4,Cjoin Burnham government as minister
OL,6,FThe Labour leader said the Cabinet he
OL,7,Fhad assembled, after purging allies of
OL,8,FSir Keir, "reflects the party, the
OL,9,Fcountry, all backgrounds", and told
OL,10,Fthose who had survived the clear-out
OL,11,Fto take it as a "major vote of
OL,12,Fconfidence".
